</style></head><body style=" font-family:'Cantarell'; font-size:10pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;">
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-size:16pt; font-weight:600;">God's heart for his church is that we would grow in faith and love as we endure to the end.</span></p>
<p style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-size:16pt; font-weight:600;"><br /></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-size:0pt; font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline;">God's heart for you is that you would grow in faith.</span></p>
<ul style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;"><li style=" font-size:0pt; font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline;" style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-weight:400; text-decoration:none;">The church's job isn't to entertain you. It is to grow you and challenge you in your faith.</span></li>
<li style=" font-size:0pt;" style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">The church shouldn't be trying to constantly make you feel better about yourself. It should be convicting and challenging to your own spiritual growth.</li>
<li style=" font-size:0pt;" style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">They are giving thanks to God for the &quot;abundant growth&quot; going on in the Thessalonian church. That kind of growth doesn't come with a lack of discipline and conviction within the church.</li>
<li style=" font-size:0pt;" style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">Growing in faith and living your daily life to worship God be that prayer, spending time in the word, serving others, etc is usually the single thing that people need to improve problems going on in their lives that they would rather blame on a diagnosis or mental issue.</li></ul>
<p style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:1; text-indent:0px; font-size:0pt;"><br /></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-size:0pt; font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline;">Personal and corporate worship should be the highest priority in our lives.</span></p>
<ul style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;"><li style=" font-size:0pt; font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline;" style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-weight:400; text-decoration:none;">The time we spend going to church and spending time in the Word is deeply important to growing in faith.</span></li>
<li style=" font-size:0pt;" style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">Coming back to church and not making excuses not to come is required for spiritual growth.</li></ul>
<p style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-size:0pt;"><br /></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-size:0pt; font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline;">God's heart for you is that you would grow in love for others.</span></p>
<ul style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;"><li style=" font-size:0pt; font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline;" style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-weight:400; text-decoration:none;">The word used here is agape and it is an action word for BEING loving whether the other person is what you personally consider loveable.</span></li>
<li style=" font-size:0pt;" style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">This love is expensive and costly. It means sacrifice of time and resources whether you have the time/resources to give or not.</li>
<li style=" font-size:0pt;" style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">Church service is an excellent way to start in this love at church.</li>
<li style=" font-size:0pt;" style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">Life groups are an excellent way to start showing this love to our community around us.</li></ul></body></html>